metadata.description: Deck the halls and get ready to dance! KIDZ BOP Christmas, compiles the most festive holiday tracks of today, including 'All I Want for Christmas Is You', 'Santa Claus Is Coming to Town', and more. Sung by kids, for kids. This Yoto Card is sure to get the entire family in the holiday spirit!
metadata.author: KIDZ BOP
